#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""kyth-exe-handler — intercept Windows .exe/.msi files and suggest Linux alternatives.

Registered as the default MIME handler for application/x-ms-dos-executable so that
double-clicking a Windows installer in Dolphin shows a curated suggestion dialog
instead of silently failing or opening a hex editor.
"""

